h2. instaling mongoDB on Ubntu 10.10

??sudo vim /etc/apt/sources.list??

add this line at the end
??deb http://downloads-distro.mongodb.org/repo/ubuntu-upstart dist 10gen??


??sudo apt-key adv --keyserver keyserver.ubuntu.com --recv 7F0CEB10
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install mongodb-10gen??

don't install just @sudo apt-get install mongodb@, you will end up with older 1.4.4 vervion of mongo, wich you will have to uninstall @apt-get remove mongo@ ; @apt-get remove mongodb-clients@

??http://localhost:28017/??

